WEBVTT

00:00:01.372 --> 00:00:04.125
This is Lakhi Ram Lohar.

00:00:04.751 --> 00:00:07.837
His job was to spray pesticide

00:00:07.837 --> 00:00:10.548
at a tea garden in West Bengal, India.

00:00:11.716 --> 00:00:13.843
Lakhi was a single father

00:00:13.843 --> 00:00:16.054
to his only daughter, Sugi.

00:00:17.472 --> 00:00:20.892
One day in 2007,

00:00:20.933 --> 00:00:22.268
Sugi went missing.

00:00:24.479 --> 00:00:28.858
Lakhiram went to the local police
to file a missing persons report,

00:00:29.984 --> 00:00:33.571
but he was unable to do so
because he was illiterate.